::Ramhorn::

Ramhorn lets out a sigh of relief as Megatron flies off.

"Megs's out of here," he says into his comm-link to Lunarpine, "The place 
looks intact."

He switches the comm to all Maximal frequences, "Whoever neutralized that 
blast, thanx!"
